<br>
Just stand there and cast your lowest level spell of the skill you want to raise over and over again.  Med, rinse, repeat.<br>
<br>
Be sure to check your skill level to see when it hits the max for your level (your level plus one times five).<br>
<br>
If you don't want to do that, there's always fishing... <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:purple;">Neewon Triumphant</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Minstrel of the <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:green;">51</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->st Song<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Jharin Apprentice<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:purple;"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=447681" target="top">Himemiya Anshy</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Magician of the <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:green;">45</span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->th Trial<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;">Members of <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.flamingshrine.com">Order of Flaming Shrine</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Erollisi Marr<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:blue;"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Zettai Unmei Mokushiroku...</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=mantria>Mantria</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 428<br> <font color=#333333>(1/13/03 9:04:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthelibrary.showAdd