<br>
My trip from Felwithe through Anotinica started when some of my friends were in Lake of Ill Omen just south of South Karanas.  I got through Kith and HHKeep just fine.  To get through High hold keep, I hired a guide to take me.  We zoned to East Karana and he told me to beware of the cliff and I started to respond which left my character running in a straight line leading over and down the cliff in East Karana.  I had no idea whether or not my corpse was recoverable.  I finally made my way down the ramp and back into the valley passing many corpses and found mine and continued on my way.<br>
<br>
Back in Butcher Block Mountains, I did exactly what Dracca did and got onto the shuttle boats that take you to the cruise ship to Firiona Vie (Dracca - this boat to firiona Vie is spectacular.  After your trip to Qeynos take a trip to Firiona Vie in Kunark)  Like Dracca I tried to jump from one shuttle boat to another and fell into the water.  Unfortunatly, I was in a new zone and didn't know I wouldn't be able to swim to a zone line.  <br>
<br>
I swam after the shuttles and then saw the big boat and swam towards it but couldn't catch it.  I improved my swimming skill for the next few hours while people in ooc and tells gave me locs to swim to.  - I can't remember if it was during this trip of another that I had my incident using Eye of zomm for the first time to spy on some red con cut throats.  Only to have them run towards my eye kill it and continue straight towards me killing me in the water at an unknown location.<br>
<br>
Nothing beats the first few months of a new EQ experience.  Every now and then I feeling something close to that when leading a group deep into a new dungeon.  But now I always have in the back of my mind that if worse comes to worse I'll pay a fraction of my fortune to summon my corpse and resurrect my sexy corpse. <p><a target="Amel Rathanon" href="http://www.familjenguild.com/dspMember.php?Name=Amel">Sage Amel Rathanon {Arch Convoker}</a><br>
