The boat leads to Firiona Vie... the Elven outpost on the continent of Kunark.  Firiona Vie is safe... the surrounding zone is not.  Invisibility and a bit of luck can lead you past the drachnids up a river to the Lake of Ill Omen ... a decent 15-25th level zone.<br>
<br>
